  "text": "The strengths of the study include the low risk of bias due to the randomized design, publication of the study protocol, the blinded measurement of the majority of the outcomes, and the blinded analysis of the outcomes. Moreover, the use of the gold standard for the measurement of plasma volume [CITATION_1] and auditing support the reliability and scientific integrity of the data.",
